Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: fps-limiter
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: Limit while loop at certain fps rate.
Home-page: http://github.com/cartovarc/fps-limiter
Author: Carlos Tovar
Author-email: cartovarc@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: fps-limiter
        ===========
        
        Limit while loop at certain fps rate
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            pip install fps-limiter
        
        Examples
        --------
        
        Example #1
        ~~~~~~~~~~
        
        .. code:: python
        
        
            from fps_limiter import LimitFPS, FPSCounter
        
            fps_limiter = LimitFPS(fps=15)
            fps_counter = FPSCounter()
        
            while True:
                if fps_limiter():
                    print("current fps: %s" % fps_counter())
        
        Example #2
        ~~~~~~~~~~
        
        .. code:: python
        
        
            from fps_limiter import LimitFPS, FPSCounter
        
            fps_limiter = LimitFPS(fps=15)
        
            while True:
                if fps_limiter():
                    print("elapsed seconds: %s" % fps_limiter.get_elapsed_seconds())
        
